{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember that because there was this lawyer in the house, a friend of my father, Moshlonko, who was later a very famous lawyer in Poland after the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was generally highly respected because he was so clever and he knew everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was absolutely of the opinion that Germans were going to be-- the Germans were invincible and the Germans were going to win the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And other than that, we-- the Germans started war with the-- with Russia, and they moved so quickly east that-- for that at this time, I think still the Russians were surrendering and going back and going back and there was no sign yet that the Germans were going to suffer any defeat at all.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were, as well, not aware at this stage, although it was already '42, that there was something worse in-- being prepared or that worse things were happening, at least not quite consciously.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe there were signs, but we didn't want to-- to listen to them then, although there was one thing, that my aunt, one of the-- Mania, who was a sister of my mother, older sister.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was a pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mentioned her before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she was a pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she was as well a quite experienced doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she went to the east as well in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But she didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was with her husband, who she married briefly before the war, when I mentioned that there was a wedding, and I went to that wedding.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So she was not so young already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She must have been in her late 30s at least.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
